  "body": "When enabling the OpenID Connect auth provider we found that auth providers are initialized almost every time kubectl needs to make a new request rather than reusing the initialized transport. @mlbiam noticed this as well as it causes kubectl to become excruciatingly slow.\r\n\r\nWill follow up with a more detailed bug report.\r\n\r\ncc @cjcullen @jlowdermilk (don't know who else to CC)",
